videos.description: Baylor gets out and running with Jonathan Motley drawing a double team and dishes it to Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Baylor's Motley draws a double team and finds the open man

videos.description: Jonathan Motley turns the ball over but comes running back down the court for the huge block.
videos.headline: Motley not allowing any easy buckets

videos.description: Ishmail Wainwright pass gets deflected but gathers it back and finds Manu Lecomte who drains the deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte hits the 3-pointer from Curry range

videos.description: Baylor's Jonathan Motley talks about his teams' win over Oklahoma and how his game has improved since last year.
videos.headline: Motley talks about how his team can still improve
